overview: Highlights from the 1991-92 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry. 46 minutes of the best hockey action. All the super hits, goals and saves of the season and playoffs. Bobby Probert and buddies drop in for a visit, plus Blue's Bloopers, and the 'Do's' and 'Don'ts' of hockey with Grapes' play book. Learn to speak hockey language with Grapes' Dictionary!! Last but not least, a few highlights from Coach's Corner. ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 4, you're going to love it!! It's a beauty!!
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 4
